    "commitMessage": "dbus-top: WIP of all currently-implemented features\n\nThis is a work in progress commit, and it's intended to show what\nthe tool can currently do, and ask for comments on design,\nimplementation and UI experience.\n\nKnown issues with the cl include:\n1) Window B (sensor details) should use the Menu class\n2) Sender PID does not fully work\n3) Column widths in Window C (stat list window) are not optimal\n\nInstruction on how to navigate the UI:\n1) Use tab to navigate each window and press enter to select\n2) Press esc key thrice to leave the current sensor selection\n3) Use enter to hide and show field in window c, and press space\n   to select.\n\nInstructions on recipe:\n1) Copy and paste the content of the .bb file into your recipe file\n2) run \"devtool modify -n dbus-top (SomePath)/openbmc-tools\n    /dbus-top/\"\n\nChange-Id: Ie261be141f001b2ad507c1c7e0548808ea933fbf\nSigned-off-by: Adedeji Adebisi <adedejiadebisi01@gmail.com>\n",
